hey there all you josh fans! ok so i have none well i forgot i had a live journal until shea reminded me i was like ow yah ha! so i got on and read all the posts i have been missing since november crazy (every thing is) so im here to tell you what i'v been up to well school is going ok ha i went to slipknot the other day it was by far the best concert iv been to i went to see lamb of god and shadows fall but slipknot was surprisingly awesome as well- well saturday april 9th is me and lindsays one year anniversary and were still doing really good so that rox tonight we have a show at equal eyes so you people out there should come watch us jam -the band is doing realy good we have new ideas every day prom is coming up thats gonna be kool and who has a limo i have a limo thats right i had to confiscate it for the better good of the people so yah thats all for now if your still alive and can read this reply something anything so i know there is life

well its been awile ..i havnt updated in like 2 months or so so sit back relax because here i go .....school is doing good got the report card for the second six weeks yestorday and im passing all my classes i have A's and B's ..one C thats weird i never thaught i would i'd be saying that thats the best grades yet cause im a ninja ..as of my health...well i weight 179 now im loosing weight but gaining musle because of the marines the recruters have been working me alot so i can be at my best when i go on july 6th its so soon this year is flying bye fast i need more time!! me and lindsay are still dating and gowing strong i love her weve been dating for 7 1/2 months now and weve faught once i think and we were mad at eachother for like an hour i cant stay mad at her shes so beautiful and energetic she makes me smile shes my everything...our band is gowing good i no longer do vocals because i baught a drum set and became the drummer because we couldnt find one we have a second guitarest now so were falling together nicely all we need now is a good vocalist does anyone know of some one who can sing metal/hardcore vocals preferably scremo metal vocals is so reply to my L.J. and tell me and ill give you my info so we can get in touch with them ....we should be playing shows come the end of december or beginning of january if we find a vocalist and all goes well... if you want a demo ask me .....well thats basicly all thats been up the past couple of months i guess any questions just ask yep thats it      peace

well here is a lil update on my life me and lindsay are doing great i love her : ) i'v got my car so we spend a lot more time together thats a + i sighned on to the marines i leave june 27th and come back sep 20 and then i leave agin oct 7 for 3 1/2 weeks then i come back to corpus because thats were im stationed then i start gowing to college im not scared i know it will be hard but it is somthing i godda do my only fear is if me and lin are still together will she wait for me because ill be gone 91 days then come back for 10 days then i leave agin for 3 1/2 weeks thats along time but i hope she waits for me to come back i dont want to loose her shes every thing to me i dont think i could loose her.. but anyway iv been working out hard trying to get in to tip top share ...our band is doing good its almost demo disk time we just have to do a lil more work on it but soon it will be out then its time to play some shows yep well thats an update on my life            

                                              peace

butane in my veins and I'm out to cut the junkie
with the plastic eyeballs, spray-paint the vegetables
dog food stalls with the beefcake pantyhose
kill the headlights and put it in neutral
stock car flamin' with a loser and the cruise control
baby's in Reno with the vitamin D 
got a couple of couches, sleep on the love-seat 
someone came in sayin' I'm insane to complain
about a shotgun wedding and a stain on my shirt
don't believe everything that you breathe 
you get a parking violation and a maggot on your sleeve
so shave your face with some mace in the dark
savin' all your food stamps and burnin' down the trailer park 
Forces of evil on a bozo nightmare 
ban all the music with a phony gas chamber 
'cuz one's got a weasel and the other's got a flag
one's on the pole, shove the other in a bag
with the rerun shows and the cocaine nose-job
the daytime crap of the folksinger slob
he hung himself with a guitar string
a slab of turkey-neck and it's hangin' from a pigeon wing
you can't write if you can't relate
trade the cash for the beef for the body for the hate
and my time is a piece of wax fallin' on a termite
that's chokin' on the splinters
